headline: DA Davidson starts coverage of Take-Two at Buy, EA at Neutral
summary: Investing.com -- DA Davidson initiated coverage of major video game stocks in notes Wednesday, assigning a Buy rating to Take-Two Interactive (NASDAQ:TTWO) and a Neutral rating to Electronic Arts (NASDAQ:EA).
